@Override public boolean equals(Object o) {     if (this == o)         return true.     if (o == null || getClass() != o.getClass())         return false.     RepositoryMetaData that = (RepositoryMetaData) o.     if (!name.equals(that.name))         return false.     if (!type.equals(that.type))         return false.     return settings.equals(that.settings). }
